name: CrossSide: The Prison
description: Immerse yourself in a dark world, full of mysteries and unforeseen events. Escape punishment and restore justice in this atmospheric VR game.

name: University Tycoon: 2019
description: Become the principal of your very own university!

name: Vector's Adventures
description: The blueprints are scattered and out of order! You must piece the worlds back together. Join Vector, a dot, the lowest form of geometry, in his adventure across the Shades of Blue as he battles a hierarchy of greater shapes. Wield the Architect's pen for puzzles and combat in the Land of Lines.

name: Essence Defenders
description:
The Void has come to devour the world - and only Essence can stop it. 
Command a fleet to protect remaining islands from Demons of the Void who come to deplete the Essence Source.

name: High Speed Extreme Bike Race Game: Space Heroes
Legendary Eleven: Epic Football
description: Legendary Eleven is an epic arcade football (soccer) game inspired by the golden age of football spanning the 70's to the 90's.

name: The Vigil Files: Case 1
description: Use VigilOS, an advanced operating system used by detectives, investigators, and secret agents all over the world, to investigate suspects, send emails and texts, make phone calls, hack into companies, and crack codes as you work to solve the mystery surrounding a man's disappearance.

name: Music vs Block: Piano Simulation Game
Silly Sailing
description:
Compete against other sassy sailors in this silly sailing game. Use your rudder and sail to find the perfect wind in this tropical paradise.
Race against other players and find out who's the silliest sailor.
Unlock continuously sillier ships (and shoes) and after a while even ships (and sofas) with multiple sails.
Behind the silly exterior exists a somewhat (not really) realistic sailing simulation.

name: Flight Simulator 0
description: Flight Simulator 0 is all about the feeling of flying. Steer a plane over an abstract landscape by simply tilting your smartphone or tablet. 26 runways wait to be discovered, some of them picturesquely located on the shores of crystal clear lakes, others well hidden between razor-sharp polygons. Just relax and follow your ears to your next destination.

name: Fear for Sale: Endless Voyage HD
Shields Up! VR
description: Shields Up! is a real-time mining construction VR strategy game. Shields Up! is a tower defense-style challenge where you land, build, mine, defend, and get out with your valuable cargo while fending off the hazards of space debris and the impending war machine.

name: A Lot Like Love
description: Rachel comes home on vacation to not only celebrate, but also get to know Jennifer's boyfriend. Neither Rachel, nor Jennifer, nor her boyfriend even imagine what this will lead to.

name: Underground Bone Marrow
description: UBM is an example of webpunk timekiller in the style of half-3D games of 80's. The essence of the game is record passage of levels. With each level enemy becomes stronger, locations bigger.

name: Prism Break
description: Get some exercise in VR with this action block busting game! You must defend yourself from the oncoming prism blocks. To do this, you must punch and /or dodge the blocks. But be careful; if a block touches you before you can punch them or if you don't punch a block hard enough, you will lose a heart.

name: RaKoval~Nya: Escape Edition
description: Our whole life is an RKN, and you are in it - Telegram. In this war, only the strongest will survive, who will be able to bypass all blockades and invasions of enemies..

name: Polyfield WW2
description: Polyfield WW2 is the Online First-Person Shooter game that describes the World War 2. In Polyfield WW2, you can choose the Axis and Allied side, and you can see and experience how destructive the war !

name: Life Goals
description:
This is a game about life. And because life is already complex enough, and games are getting harder to make, let's make it simpler and project everything onto one dimension. 
In 1D, choices seem simpler, but it does not make life much easier. 
Grow up. Overcome all obstacles. Reach your Life Goals.

name: The Big Three
description: The Big Three is a joyful twin stick shooter game and like the Guerrilla war . At the verge of victory during WWII, with the hope of catching the Big Three in meeting and turning the table, Hitler sent Special Forces to attack Teheran. The player will play one of the Big Three. Under the assists of Kai-shek Military Transport, the player will at last break through the close siege of Nazi and catch Hitler, like in the classic game Guerilla War and Commando .

name: The Player RPG
description: Enter the world of old school 2D RPG games, but with a different approach. This time you as the player know you are playing a game, are NPCs just that? Does the world even matters?

name: Megaplex Manager
description:
MEGAPLEX MANAGER is a free simulation and strategy browser game where you manage the economy of a virtual cinema (movie theater). The gameplay is a mix between a fantasy boxoffice and cinema tycoon. 
 
You get to schedule movies, purchase screens or refill snacks to meet equilibrium in supply and demand. 
 
Will you become the next multiplex mogul?

name: Kick BuddyMan 2
description: kick buddyhero adventures is a free game, full of adventures

name: Fleet Force
description: You have a fleet and you must control the enemy. Play over 24 levels and 8 ships with configurable weapons against other fleets in a distant galaxy.

name: Steamboat Billy: The Curse of the Leviathan
description: Most succinctly described as Zelda: Windwaker meets Pokemon, Steamboat Billy is a single-player adventure-rpg set in an old Disney-like universe in which you must befriend monsters while sailing the dark seas in order to survive, rebuild and bring back color to the world you once knew!

name: The Wisdom and/or Madness of Crowds
Forradia Forever
description: Forradia Forever is an independently developed MMORPG in a fantasy setting. In the world of Forradia endless adventures awaits you which will help you on your journey to become a legend. Team up with players from all over the world to overcome even the toughest challenges.

name: King's Escape
description:
Help the king to run away from his enemies who surrounded his castle. he needs YOU to guide him through the secret door of his castle and run away from enemies by dodging their attacks and breaking down the platforms and reach to the bottom of the castle.
using king powers like a fireball to break down platforms and enemies to get more scores and diamonds. Collect as many coins & diamonds to buy more powers and get more scores.

name: TrollFace Quest: Horror 3
description: TrollFace is always delighting us with new parodies of famous movies, games or TV series. Unusual heroes like to joke on everyone, and everyone can be a victim of another prank. In the game "TrollFace Quest: Horror 3", you will plunge into an atmosphere of fear, which will become a hilarious farce with the help of trolls. In this game, new horror movies, as well as classic retro horror movies, come under the banter of bullies. If you've been frightened by such movies before, now they'll make you laugh. Granny Babka, Dracula, The Mummy, Resident Evil, The Ring and other already classic horror industry movies will be the center of your fun and make you develop your logical abilities. Each level has two options for the development of the plot. Your goal is to find just the right solution to the episode and you can move on to the next fun level.On the first level you will meet Granny's grandmother. Crazy old woman meets you with a club, and is waiting for your actions. What to do will be up to you to decide whether you can continue your adventures in Trollface Quest. Enjoy the game and good luck!

name: Wrassling
description: Wrassling is the national sport of Slamdovia, champion Wrasslers are regarded as the strongest athletes in the world.

name: The mother of the bird men
The Perfect Tower
description: Defend, upgrade, repeat! This idle strategy game combines a tower defense theme with incremental gameplay, resource management, and roguelike aspects. Fend off relentless waves, upgrade strategically, and experience the addictive thrill of ever-rising numbers.

name: Easy Joe 4
description: Easy Joe goes on a wild adventure again. In Easy Joe 4 the bunny sees some trouble coming his way. You have to help him to solve riddles to complete each stage.

name: Iridescent
description: Use the spectrite stones and your trusty slingshot in your quest to find the cure.

name: Building Rush 2
description:
You are the boss! Manage the manufacturing and delivery of building materials to construction sites in multiple cities.

Build and upgrade your plants and construction fleets to produce, ship and sell the building materials that your plants generate. Deliver the goods as quickly and efficiently as possible to keep your customers happy and earn bigger bonuses. Watch out as your competitors will also set up factories to try and steal your business!

Earning medals and achievements will award you with money that you can spend to upgrade your facilities and fleets.
The better your performance on a level, the more money you'll earn to spend on upgrades. Replay completed levels to improve your scores and earn more money for upgrades!

It's time to get to work!

name: Turbo Town
description:
Did you miss him? Yeah, don't answer that...
Join Mr. Business on his quest to overcome his daddy issues by overcompensating for absolutely everything! Build the biggest town with the longest towers and most materialistic materials! Watch each building automatically consume and produce a variety of resources! The only finger you'll ever have to raise is your index finger, because exercise is a waste of time meant for the unwashed masses! Wallow in narcissism and shower yourself with boosts that come from the most golden of chests, then fill the hole in your heart by equipping them to buildings! Feel the joy of being Mr. Business' totally not imaginary subordinate, because you're the only thing keeping him from realizing he's another piece of detritus slowly spiraling around the toilet bowl of life!

name: The Final Earth
description:
The Final Earth is a mini city builder/simulation on a small planet.

It's 2100 and Earth has been made uninhabitable by devastating climate change. As a great scientist, you have prepared, of course. Over the last fifty years, you built a teleporter and transported yourself and some materials across the galaxy to the only habitable planet you could find. Unfortunately, it's pretty small. Can you build a new society on this planet?

name: Star Quest: TCG
description: A fun and cunning campaign that brings you into the universe of Star Quest: TCG. Your spaceship has crashed in a mysterious planet during a space battle, and you have to start over. Defeat your opponents, recruit units, build a fleet and prepare yourself for the ultimate space card battle.

name: Kitty Catsanova
description: Kitty Catsanova is the premier Idle Cat Dating Sim! Collect adorable kitties and win their hearts by taking them out on lavish dates, crafting exquisite gifts, and buying them wondrous presents. Manage your time carefully, since you don't want any kitties to get lonely!

It's a spin-off of the serie Medieval Cop.

description: A new twist on an age-old game, Bullet Chess is a top-down roguelike shooter where all of the enemies move and attack like chess pieces. Your weapons are also inspired by chess pieces, so everything is intuitive and easy to pick up. Beware though, it gets very hectic very quickly!

name: WGT Baseball MLB
description: An official Major League Baseball licensed game with Hall of Fame MLB players and all your favorite MLB teams in turbo time! This is not a hardcore simulation game, just simple, clean, fast baseball fun, combining interactive batting action and strategic management. Collect Hall of Fame MLB players, hit homeruns and dominate your League Division. Featuring all 30 MLB teams including: Cardinals, Cubs, Dodgers, Giants, Mets, Orioles, Phillies, Rangers, Red Sox, Royals, Tigers, Yankees and more...

description: Challenge your equation solving speed in this fast paced math game. Each round consists of three math problems: addition, subtraction, multiplication. You must select the correct answer in the limited amount of time that would correctly answer the equation.

name: Word Swipe
description: If you like solving various puzzles and are looking for a new and exciting online game, welcome to Word Swipe. On the screen in front of you will be a playing field divided into equal number of cells and filled with letters of English alphabet. Your task is to clear the field of letters. To do this you need to look carefully through the field and find the letters next to each other, which can form a word. Then simply connect these letters with a line using your mouse. As soon as you do this, these letters will disappear from the playing field and you will get points. Thus, solving puzzles and guessing words, you will gradually clear the field of letters.

name: Piano Game X
description:
Piano Game X is a musical and memory game! The game plays a note and you have to guess and play it on the piano. If you guess right other notes will be added creating long melodies. Will you remember the whole sequence? 
Challenge your friends, train your hear and discover always new tunes!
